                    },
                    "locales": {
                        "en": {
                            "text": "<p>I’m a {{Full Stack Engineer}} with [[5 years of experience]] building real-time communication and cloud-native applications across telecom, SaaS, and medical devices.</p><p>I am experienced in React/Angular, Node.js, and GCP, with a track record of improving latency, reliability, and developer productivity in production systems serving thousands of daily sessions.</p><p>I look forward to collaborating [[with you!]]</p>"
                        },
                        "zh": {
                            "text": "<p>我是一名拥有 [[5 年经验]] 的 {{全栈工程师}}，擅长在电信、SaaS 和医疗设备领域构建实时通信和云原生应用。</p><p>我精通 React/Angular、Node.js 和 GCP（谷歌云平台），在改善支撑每日数千次会话的生产系统延迟、可靠性和开发者生产力方面拥有出色的成绩。</p><p>期待与您 [[合作！]]</p>"
                        }
                    }
                }
